beer.beer_description:
English description (German below):

A guide to be fruity: Open the balcony door, free your mind. Into the hammock, out of the daily hustle. Crown caps down, exotic tastes in. Sounds OMG? But it's IPA!

Satte Hopfenbombe mit geschmeidiger Bittere.
Anleitung zum fruchtig sein: Balkontür auf, Kopp zu. In die Hängematte rein, aus’m Alltagstrott raus. Kronkorken runter, exotische Geschmäcker rein. Sounds OMG? Is aber IPA!

items.badge_description: Looking for more kick than a session beer, but want to be able to stay for a few rounds? You have to keep it in the middle. That's 470 beers with an ABV greater than 5% and less than 10%.  Try 5 more for Level 95!

items.badge_description: While spontaneity can be fun, sometimes you want to make sure your adventure will rock. Checkout the menu at an Untappd Verified Venue before visiting and know exactly what’s on tap! That's 160 check-ins at venue that is verified. Try 5 more for Level 33!

Fresh from the tap is one of the best ways to enjoy a beer. Just try to use a glass and not drink directly from the tap, as tempting as it may be. That's 65 checkins with the serving style of Draft. Try 5 more for Level 14!

items.badge_description: Your quest to quench your thirst leaves no stone unturned! That's at least 20 distinct venues!

There's beer in them thar hills! You're setting off on your journey through the world of beer, but be sure to take a little time to get to know each brewery as you go. That's a beer from 35 different breweries. Try 5 more for Level 8!

Fresh from the tap is one of the best ways to enjoy a beer. Just try to use a glass and not drink directly from the tap, as tempting as it may be. That's 25 checkins with the serving style of Draft. Try 5 more for Level 6!

Everyone loves fresh beer, but obviously not as much as you do. You went straight to the source. 

That's a beer at 5 different venues categorized as a Brewery, Cidery or Meadery. Visit 5 more for Level 2!
